{"id":289659,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/奇闻录-盛世一景-4-18/","date":"2013-04-18T18:45:19Z","modified":"2013-04-18T18:45:19Z","title":"奇闻录 | 盛世一景 4-18","content":"<p><p>4月16日早晨，郑州石佛村村口，商丘农民赵长永在当临时人体模特。这之前，他从来没听说过“裸模”这职业。“我真是羞死了，恨不得立马逃跑。”考虑许久，赵长永还是脱下了衣服。<span></span></p>\n<p>11年前，他的儿子被查出患有再生障碍性贫血。5年前，女儿被查出患有白血病。为给孩子看病，原本还算富裕的他已经花了60余万元。为筹钱给孩子治病，47岁的他不得不成为一名“裸模”。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/luomo111.jpg\"><img src=\"https://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/luomo111.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-15105\" /></a></p>\n<p>图片来源：CFP</p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<h3>猜你喜欢</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://qiwen.lu/13627.html\">盛世一景 3-25</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://qiwen.lu/13644.html\">盛世一景 3-26</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://qiwen.lu/14643.html\">盛世一景 4-11</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://qiwen.lu/13473.html\">盛世一景 3-22</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://qiwen.lu/14803.html\">盛世一景 4-15</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":1004,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[20387,19196]}